
                         An Oscilloscope Calibrator.
                         ---------------------------


    Minimum operating requirements are:-
    ------------------------------------

    1) Standard Amiga A500 with 512Kb or more of memory.
    2) Workbench 1.3x.
    3) An external floppy disk drive is required.
    4) OCS.
    5) The mouse is optional.
    6) The software has NOT been tested on an Amiga A1000.
    7) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 1.2x or less.
    8) The software has NOT been tested on Workbench 3.1x or greater.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------

    General information:-
    ---------------------

    This tool is the start of the next generation of projects. It is to whet
    your appetite for ~TestGear4A.lha~ and ~TestGear4A.readme~ which will be
    a Digital Storage Oscilloscope. Some previous projects may be used to
    set up this Oscilloscope.

    This software was written using ACE basic compiler and some assembler.

